Challenges

During Business OSINT investigations, common challenges include:

Outdated public information

Multiple company domains

Incomplete records

Third-party hosted services

Similar company names

Information overload



---

Best Practices

Use only publicly available information.

Respect privacy and legal boundaries.

Never attempt unauthorized access.

Verify findings through multiple trusted sources.

Maintain proper documentation.

Follow ethical OSINT principles.



